<br>
Reckon there's a couple of dieties that could work similarly (all Erollisi group spreading the love, anyone? *chuckle*) but Rodcet Nife warriors and rogues I'm betting are relatively rare... <br>
<br>
My moody l'il ranger takes up more of my playtime than I really even should allow, though. <br>
<br>
Also always wished I had the time to organize a wolf-pack of Ebon Mask rogues who played off the various Teir'dal houses and such... <br>
<br>
Anyone else have big ideas they'd try out if they suddenly had an eighth day a week? <br>
<br>
