<br>
Our guild picked another server to try random rp ideas and storylines. Besides being teased or stared at by the server population, we have a blast heh. I play a young female gnome enchantress who is borderline insane (my mom always said I was special!) and who 'makes friends' (charms random critters) constantly, changes into objects and literally thinks she's become a chair. or a fireplace. or a barrel. <br>
<br>
I also play an ogress youngster who wandered into the swamp, got lost, and latched onto the first person she saw, a level headed halfling. She looks up to him and follows him around, and doesn't understand why he gets upset when she bashes a random dwarf up 'because I like this pretty axe and it's mine now!'. She looks hurt when he tries to shoo her away, and smaches anything that harms him into little bits.<br>
<br>
Yeah not enough hours in a day... <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
